        <mxCell id="V99MnyYNydJ-gA_DM3Ux-37" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="Prediabetes often has no symptoms. A normal A1C is below 5.7. Above that, the risk of developing type 2 diabetes increases each year without changes." vertex="1">
