        <mxCell id="V99MnyYNydJ-gA_DM3Ux-38" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="About 96 million American adults have prediabetes. More than 80 percent of them don&#39;t know it. It is common, and it is also serious." vertex="1">
