        <mxCell id="V99MnyYNydJ-gA_DM3Ux-39" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontStyle=1" value="&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Small swaps add up. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Diluting a sugar sweetened beverage with a diet beverage slowly over time can make this shift subtle.&lt;/span&gt;" vertex="1">
