        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="889IyH6keWciR2a_tIQm-2" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="A1C numbers in the prediabetes range tend to rise over time without changes. For some people, cutting one sugary drink a day slowed or reversed that trend." vertex="1">
